reviews.review_text:
Best source This AUD has the best sound quality of all of the sources listed, including the current Charlie Miller SBD (which is quite flat). 

Great versions of all the songs, especially Here Comes Sunshine. Is this an incredible show, no, but for those of us who appreciate '93, you will enjoy it. Lightning Bolt recently debuted and played in this show. 

Great tape, as always Todd
